<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="do.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="services">
            <h1><span>WHAT WE DO AT PIERC</span></h1>
        </section>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i>
                    <h3>Startup <span> Counselling & Handhold Support</span></h3>
                    <p>To ensure that whatever entrepreneurial idea is in the mind of the student directly meets the
                        current needs of the world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <h3>Access to Pre-Seed & Seed Grants & Funding<span> Opportunities</span></h3>
                    <p>Grants/Schemes, Private Seed, Angel & VC Funding, Short-term & Long-term Loans.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
                    <h3>Co-working Space & Allied<span>Resources</span></h3>
                    <p>Flexi & Dedicated Work Desk, Meeting Lounges, Seminar Hall & Allied Resources.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <h3>Startup<span>Programs</span></h3>
                    <p>Uniquely designed programs to help students in their entrepreneurial journey - from idea to
                        growth stage. Some programs are Incubation Program, Growthpad Program and Need-Based Support
                        Program.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i>
                    <h3>Product<span>Development</span></h3>
                    <p>Access to FABLAB and other prototyping facilities to help innovators bring their ideas into the
                        real world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-connectdevelop"></i>
                    <h3>Mentor <span> Connect</span></h3>
                    <p>Facilitating easy connection of vast & experienced pool of startup mentors and domain experts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    <h3>Startup Community  <span>Connect</span></h3>
                    <p>Networking opportunities to connect with ecosystem stakeholders.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <h3>Startup  <span>Events</span></h3>
                    <p>Access to various Startup Events, Startup Festival, Demo Days, Startup Expo, Idea pitching and E-Talks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
